data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This totally updated, 2-story beauty offers a perfect blend of sophistication, luxury, and space. With 4 bedrooms, 2 full baths, 1 half bath, a 2-car garage, and a 2-car carport, this 3,468 sqft residence is a true gem. As you step inside, you'll be immediately captivated by the stunning tile that graces the main floor, creating an elegant and welcoming atmosphere. The formal dining room is ideal for hosting dinner parties or enjoying family gatherings. The large living room boasts tall ceilings, filling the space with natural light and providing an airy feel. It's the perfect spot to relax and unwind with loved ones. The oversized master suite is a private oasis, featuring a retreat-style master bath complete with a separate tub and shower. Not to mention the generous walk-in closets that cater to all your storage needs. Dont miss the game room space! Equipped with a wet bar and butcher block countertops, it's a haven for entertainers. Come check it out!
